#: templates/main/base.html:235
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Global Technology Leading PV Enterprise DAH Solar Co., Ltd.&nbsp;focuses on "
"the R&amp;D, manufacturing, and sales of high-efficiency power generation PV"
" modules, integrated PV systems, and solar energy storage systems. DAH Solar"
" committees to provide better solar solutions innovatively. With more and "
"more needs for clean energy, DAH Solar continues to bring a more efficient, "
"convenient, and reliable series of PV products to global users. "
"Technological innovation and patented products With our leading "
"technological innovation and excellent product quality, we enable global "
"users more conveniently and stably to obtain efficient clean solar energy. "
"We have 200 patented technologies used in our PV products. Our global "
"patented product Full-Screen PV module achieves front A-side frameless "
"design, which increases power generation by 6%%-15%% (field test result "
"published by TUV Nord) compared to the regular PV modules. The world's first"
" integrated PV system, SolarUnit, could maximize the installation area of "
"the rooftop. SolarUnit made the integrated design of modules and inverters "
"come true. SolarUnit provides users with a more efficient, convenient, "
"safer, and beautiful residential PV system. SolarUnit promotes PV products "
"in the era of home PV appliances. World Recognized PV Supplier DAH Solar's "
"products have been sold in more than 100 countries and regions around the "
"world. In Latin America, we have become the TOP 3 well-known PV companies in"
" Brazil. In Europe, the demand for our innovative products, Full-Screen PV "
"Modules, is exceeding supplies. Besides, to provide better service to global"
" customers, we have established our warehouses in many countries and "
"regions, like the EU stock in Rotterdam in the Netherlands. In addition, we "
"have established very convenient purchase channels for global consumers. "
"Customers can purchase DAH Solar’s products through distributors or official"
" websites and E-commercial platforms. Social Responsibilities DAH Solar’s "
"Solar Cells, Modules, and Inverters R&amp;D and Production Factories Bases "
"not only attract a large number of local high-end technical talents but also"
" creates more than 2,000 job positions for local residents. Every year, we "
"hold many social activities, such as donations to charities, responses to "
"the Covid-19 pandemic, contributing to community growth, etc. to advocate "
"for social development. Our ultimate goal is to embrace the era of clean "
"energy to protect the environment and the behalf of mankind. Employee "
"Development DAH Solar is committed to creating a better career development "
"platform for our employees. We seek equity for all genders and ages in the "
"workplace. DAH Solar offers our employees a free team-building trip, "
"annually. We believe that refreshing is another path to creation. DAH Solar "
"is also concerned about the health condition of our employees. That's why we"
" provide our employees with free health checks and a full package of "
"healthcare. At DAH Solar, we treat our employees not only as team assets but"
" as our own families."
msgstr ""
"Global Technology Leading PV Enterprise DAH Solar Co., Ltd. &nbsp; Yuqori "
"samarali energiya ishlab chiqarish PV modullari, integratsiyalangan PV "
"tizimlari va quyosh energiyasini saqlash tizimlarini Ar-ge, ishlab chiqarish"
" va sotishga e'tibor qaratadi. DAH Quyosh qo'mitalari innovatsion ravishda "
"yaxshiroq quyosh echimlarini taqdim etish uchun. Toza energiyaga bo'lgan "
"ehtiyoj tobora ortib borayotgani sababli, DAH Solar global "
"foydalanuvchilarga yanada samarali, qulay va ishonchli PV mahsulotlarini "
"taqdim etishda davom etmoqda. Texnologik innovatsiyalar va patentlangan "
"mahsulotlar Bizning etakchi texnologik innovatsiyalarimiz va mukammal "
"mahsulot sifati bilan biz global foydalanuvchilarga samarali toza quyosh "
"energiyasini olish uchun qulayroq va barqaror imkoniyat beramiz. Bizning PV "
"mahsulotlarimizda ishlatiladigan 200 ta patentlangan texnologiya mavjud. "
"Bizning global patentlangan mahsulotimiz Full-Screen PV moduli oldingi A "
"tomoni ramkasiz dizaynga erishadi, bu oddiy PV modullariga nisbatan energiya"
" ishlab chiqarishni 6%%-15%% ga oshiradi (TUV Nord tomonidan chop etilgan "
"dala sinovi natijasi). Dunyodagi birinchi integratsiyalashgan PV tizimi "
"SolarUnit uyingizda o'rnatish maydonini maksimal darajada oshirishi mumkin. "
"SolarUnit modullar va invertorlarning integratsiyalashgan dizaynini amalga "
"oshirdi. SolarUnit foydalanuvchilarga yanada samaraliroq, qulayroq, "
"xavfsizroq va chiroyli turar-joy PV tizimini taqdim etadi. SolarUnit uy PV "
"asboblari davrida PV mahsulotlarini targ'ib qiladi. Dunyoda tan olingan PV "
"yetkazib beruvchi DAH Solar mahsulotlari dunyoning 100 dan ortiq "
"mamlakatlari va mintaqalarida sotilgan. Lotin Amerikasida biz Braziliyadagi "
"TOP 3 ta taniqli PV kompaniyalariga aylandik. Evropada bizning innovatsion "
"mahsulotlarimizga, To'liq ekranli PV modullariga bo'lgan talab takliflardan "
"oshib ketadi. Bundan tashqari, global mijozlarga yaxshiroq xizmat ko'rsatish"
" uchun biz Gollandiyaning Rotterdam shahridagi EI aktsiyalari kabi ko'plab "
"mamlakatlar va mintaqalarda o'z omborlarimizni tashkil etdik. Bundan "
"tashqari, biz global iste'molchilar uchun juda qulay xarid kanallarini "
"yaratdik. Mijozlar DAH Solar mahsulotlarini distribyutorlar yoki rasmiy veb-"
"saytlar va elektron tijorat platformalari orqali sotib olishlari mumkin. "
"Ijtimoiy mas'uliyat DAH Quyoshning quyosh batareyalari, modullari va "
"invertorlari Ar-ge va ishlab chiqarish zavodlari bazalari nafaqat ko'plab "
"mahalliy yuqori darajadagi texnik iste'dodlarni jalb qiladi, balki mahalliy "
"aholi uchun 2000 dan ortiq ish o'rinlarini yaratadi. Biz har yili ijtimoiy "
"rivojlanishni targ'ib qilish uchun xayriya tashkilotlariga xayr-ehsonlar, "
"Covid-19 pandemiyasiga qarshi kurash, jamiyatning o'sishiga hissa qo'shish "
"va boshqalar kabi ko'plab ijtimoiy tadbirlarni o'tkazamiz. Bizning yakuniy "
"maqsadimiz atrof-muhitni va insoniyat nomini himoya qilish uchun toza "
"energiya davrini qabul qilishdir. Xodimlarni rivojlantirish DAH Solar "
"xodimlarimiz uchun yaxshiroq martaba rivojlantirish platformasini yaratishga"
" intiladi. Biz ish joyida barcha jinslar va yoshdagilar uchun tenglikni "
"qidiramiz. DAH Solar o'z xodimlariga har yili bepul jamoa qurish sayohatini "
"taklif qiladi. Biz yangilanishni yaratishning yana bir yo'li deb "
"hisoblaymiz. DAH Solar ham xodimlarimizning sog'lig'i haqida qayg'uradi. "
"Shuning uchun biz xodimlarimizni bepul tibbiy ko'rikdan o'tkazamiz va tibbiy"
" yordamning to'liq paketini taqdim etamiz. DAH Solar kompaniyasida biz "
"xodimlarimizga nafaqat jamoaning aktivi, balki o'z oilamiz kabi munosabatda "
"bo'lamiz."

