#: templates/main/home.html:257
#, python-format
msgid ""
" Being established in 2009, DAH Solar is an innovation-driven and "
"technology-leading company in PV product manufacturing.The production "
"capacity in 2024 will reach 6GW solar cells,10GW PV modules, 300,000 sets "
"SolarUnit, 5GW silicon wafers and 10GW vertical integration manufacturing "
"base under construction, Solar Unit. DAH Solar contributes to providinghigh-"
"efficiencyPVmodules,high-qualitysolarcells,high-techintegrated solars "
"ystems, and high-value energy storage for our value dcustomers. DAH Solar’s "
"products have been sold to more than 120 countries and regions around the "
"world includingGermany, Netherlands, Spain, Brazil, Mexico, Australia, Japan"
" and soon. &nbsp; Technology innovation has been the most important driving "
"force of the development of DAH Solar. DAH Solar invests more than 15%% "
"annually in&nbsp; research and development. DAH Solar is the founder and the"
" master of the Full-Screen PV Module.The Full-Screen PV Module which has no "
"frame on all sides on the front holds a global patent over 18 countries and "
"regions, it can increase the power generation by 6-15%%. Besides, DAH Solar "
"invents the world’s first integrated PV system, SolarUnit. DAH Solar’s "
"products have international authoritative certifications such as TUV, IEC, "
"CE,and INMETRO,domestic industry certifications such as CQC, Leader, "
"ISO9001, ISO14001, ISO45001, etc. DAH Solar will always regard the user "
"demand as the key focus of product research and innovation and keep on "
"bringing more efficient, stable and intelligent photovoltaicproducts."
msgstr ""
"2009-yilda tashkil etilgan DAH Solar — fotoelektr (PV) mahsulotlarini ishlab"
" chiqarishda innovatsiyalarga tayanuvchi va texnologik yetakchi kompaniya "
"hisoblanadi. 2024-yilda ishlab chiqarish quvvati: 6 GVt quyosh elementlari, "
"10 GVt PV modullari, 300 000 to'plam SolarUnit, 5 GVt kremniy plastinalari "
"va qurilayotgan 10 GVtli vertikal integratsiyalashgan bazani tashkil etadi. "
"DAH Solar mijozlarga yuqori samarali PV modullari, sifatli quyosh "
"elementlari, yuqori texnologiyali quyosh tizimlari va energiya saqlash "
"yechimlarini taqdim etadi. Kompaniya mahsulotlari dunyoning 120 dan ortiq "
"mamlakatlarida, jumladan Germaniya, Niderlandiya, Ispaniya, Braziliya, "
"Meksika, Avstraliya va Yaponiyada sotilmoqda. Texnologik innovatsiyalar DAH "
"Solar rivojlanishining asosiy kuchi bo'lib, kompaniya har yili R&D sohasiga "
"15%% dan ortiq sarmoya kiritadi. DAH Solar — ramkasiz to'liq ekranli (Full-"
"Screen PV Module) modulining asoschisi. Ushbu texnologiya 18 ta davlatda "
"patentlangan bo'lib, energiya ishlab chiqarishni 6-15%% ga oshirishi mumkin."
" Shuningdek, kompaniya dunyodagi birinchi integratsiyalashgan SolarUnit "
"tizimini ixtiro qildi. Mahsulotlar TUV, IEC, CE, INMETRO kabi xalqaro va "
"CQC, ISO9001, ISO14001 kabi sanoat sertifikatlariga ega. DAH Solar doimo "
"foydalanuvchi talabini e'tiborda tutib, yanada samarali va aqlli fotoelektr "
"mahsulotlarini yetkazib berishda davom etadi."

