#: templates/main/home.html:274
msgid ""
"DAH Solar has 4 high-end technology factories with fully automatic workshops"
" and equipment. Annually DAH Solar’s intelligent factories could "
"produce&nbsp;5.5 GW capacity for TOPCon solar cells, 10 GW TOPCon PV "
"modules(over all is 2024 simiyearly production goal).&nbsp;&nbsp;DAH Solar "
"is conjecting the cultivation of the mass production of N-type PV modules, "
"Integrative microinverters, and solar storage in the next few years. DAH "
"Solar aims to provide a low-carbon lifestyle, so we maintain our intelligent"
" factories environment friendly, low-carbon, and green.&nbsp; DAH factories "
"maintain high productivity by equipping factories with advanced automatic "
"equipment. We grasp the leading manufacturing technique. DAH Solar "
"committees provide high-quality PV products, so we have strict inspections "
"and quality control protocols. Our highly efficient logistics guarantee the "
"fastest delivery to customers all over the world."
msgstr ""
"DAH Solar to'liq avtomatik ustaxonalar va uskunalarga ega 4 ta yuqori "
"texnologiyali zavodga ega. Har yili DAH Solar aqlli zavodlari TOPCon quyosh "
"batareyalari uchun 5,5 GVt quvvat, 10 GVt TOPCon PV modullarini ishlab "
"chiqarishi mumkin (barchasi 2024 yilga mo'ljallangan ishlab chiqarish "
"maqsadi). DAH Solar kelgusi bir necha yil ichida N-tipli PV modullarini, "
"Integrativ mikroinverterlarni va quyosh batareyasini saqlashni ommaviy "
"ishlab chiqarishni o'stirishni taxmin qilmoqda. DAH Solar kam uglerodli "
"turmush tarzini ta'minlashga qaratilgan, shuning uchun biz aqlli "
"zavodlarimizni atrof-muhitga mos, kam uglerodli va yashil rangda saqlaymiz. "
"DAH zavodlari zavodlarni ilg'or avtomatik uskunalar bilan jihozlash orqali "
"yuqori mahsuldorlikni saqlaydi. Biz etakchi ishlab chiqarish texnologiyasini"
" tushunamiz. DAH Quyosh qo'mitalari yuqori sifatli PV mahsulotlarini taqdim "
"etadi, shuning uchun bizda qattiq tekshiruvlar va sifat nazorati "
"protokollari mavjud. Bizning yuqori samarali logistikamiz butun dunyo "
"bo'ylab mijozlarga eng tez yetkazib berishni kafolatlaydi."

